<div id="attachment_247457" style="width: 1536px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-247457" class="wp-image-247457 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/hanson-6.jpg" alt="an impressionistic painting of a Texan grassland landscape with emphasis on a large, cloudy, dramatic sky at sunset" width="1526" height="1920" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/hanson-6.jpg 1526w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/hanson-6-640x805.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/hanson-6-960x1208.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/hanson-6-1221x1536.jpg 1221w" sizes="(max-width: 1526px) 100vw, 1526px"></p>
